# 💰 Finance Tracker App

A **personal finance management app** built using **Flutter**, **Dart**, and **Firebase**. This app helps users track income, categorize expenses, and manage budgets efficiently.

---

## 📱 Features

- 📊 **Dashboard**: Overview of monthly income and expenses
- 💸 **Expense Categories**: Food, Shopping, Entertainment, etc.
- 🔄 **Add Income / Expense** with date and description
- 🧮 **Budget Management**: Set monthly limits
- 🔐 **Login / Signup** with Firebase
- 📈 **Graphical Reports** (planned in future)

---

## 🧰 Tools & Technologies

| Component        | Technology           |
|------------------|-----------------------|
| Frontend         | Flutter               |
| Programming Lang | Dart                  |
| Database         | Firebase (planned)    |
| IDE              | Visual Studio Code    |
| State Mgmt       | Provider (setup ready) |

---


```

---

## 🛠️ How to Run This Project

### Step 1: Clone the Repo

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/finance-tracker-app.git
cd finance-tracker-app
```

### Step 2: Get Dependencies

```bash
flutter pub get
```

### Step 3: Run the App

```bash
flutter run
```

Make sure emulator or real device is connected.

---

## 🔒 Firebase Integration (Optional)

Firebase structure is prepared but not configured. Add your `google-services.json` and set up Firebase Auth + Firestore for full functionality.

